attributes.title: Week #44
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff kick off the brand new year with a fresh new AHWU. Stay tuned for news on the Nintendo 3DS, Mass Effect 2, Dead space 2, a hint of future AH videos and more!

attributes.title: Week #45
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff take you through another spiffy AHWU for the early weeks of 2011! Trivia question: how many "Binary Days" are left in 2011 Go!

attributes.title: Week #46
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back, fresh-faced and ready to face the world! Hooray AHWU!

attributes.title: Week #48
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you some fresh new AHWU and gaming news for the last week of January 2011. It's like we hardly knew ye. Watch for this week's new releases and news on Sony's new PSP2, the next Angry Birds and more!

attributes.title: Week #49
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with some fresh new AHWU for you and your loved ones. Today they go over "You Don't Know Jack," a Superbowl surprise and more!

attributes.title: Week #50
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff wish you a special Valentines Day on this rosy new AHWU. Learn about Marvel Vs. Capcom 3, Bowling, Balls, Halo: Reach Map Packs and more!

attributes.title: Week #51
attributes.description: Jack is flying solo this week for AHWU. Spread some love and gaming news by watching...won't you

attributes.title: Week #52
attributes.description: Celebrate with us as we ring in our first year of AHWU. Join Jack as he goes through this week's releases and news and shares some community-submitted clips! We love you all!

attributes.title: Week #53
attributes.description: Jack is still solo this week for AHWU but he has a request for help! Watch and learn how you can be a part of AHWU in the future!

attributes.title: Week #54
attributes.description: Jack is back (still solo) to bring you news for Pi week! Listen to his PAX-torn voice as he talks about this week's games and more!

attributes.title: Week #55
attributes.description: Jack, Geoff and special guest Michael (star of Rage Quit) provide you with some fascinating news and new release dates for your favorite titles! OMG! Holy crap! It's Monday, Monday, gotta get AHWU on Monday!

attributes.title: Week #56
attributes.description: Geoff pretty much doesn't work at the office any more, so Jack is back yet again, flying solo on AHWU. This week he goes over Need for Speed: Shift 2, WWE All-Stars, Dynasty Warriors 7 and more! Look for super special cameos.

attributes.title: Week #61
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff kick start the month of May with yet another fantastic AHWU. Enjoy!

attributes.title: Week #62
attributes.description: Geoff and a sickly Jack take on this week's new releases and news. Come for the game information, stay for the crazy amount of awesome intros!

attributes.title: Week #63
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver you the freshest news in this week's AHWU. Join them as they talk about Modern Warfare 3, Chrono Trigger and have a few laughs in the process.

attributes.title: Week #65
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff fight off post-RTX hangovers with a fresh batch of gaming news in this week's AHWU.

attributes.title: Week #66
attributes.description: Jack is flying solo out in Los Angeles for E3, but that won't stop him from putting out a brand new AHWU! He takes a look at this week's games and all of the happenings from the Microsoft E3 Press Conference!

attributes.title: Week #67
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back in action, with Geoff being cold and Jack being happy. This week's releases include the long-awaited Duke Nukem Forever!

attributes.title: Week #68
attributes.description: While Geoff is away, the Joel will play. This week Jack does his best to wrangle Joel in to doing AHWU with him. It goes about as well as you could expect. Stay tuned for Shadows of the Damned, Halo CE Anniversary, Kinect and more!

attributes.title: Week #69
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff take on the elusive AHWU #69. This week they look at Microsoft's Summer of Games, the newest Call of Duty: Black Ops DLC and more!

attributes.title: Week #70
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back after vacation with a fresh new AHWU. Today's AHWU brings forth news on upcoming games like NCAA Football 12, Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2 and much more!

attributes.title: Week #71
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver a fresh pile of gaming news and releases as well as announce the next Game Fails contest! This week we are looking for the best Left 4 Dead (1 or 2) fail to celebrate the new DLC!

attributes.title: Week #72
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff tackle some important issues in this week's AHWU. Namely, what kind of cake (or pie) to eat during our Three Year Anniversary on Thursday. While they fight about it, why don't you come and join us in a community playdate! We're checking out different games every day this week.

attributes.title: Week #73
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you the freshest game news in this week's AHWU. Join them as they talk about upcoming gaming events, new DLC, XBLA titles, Minecraft, iam8bit and more!

attributes.title: Week #74
attributes.description: Jack and Joel attempt to take you through a very very slow week in AHWU. With only one XBLA title hitting, this may be the slowest week ever. Also, don't forget the Freddy Krueger DLC hitting on Tuesday for Mortal Kombat!

attributes.title: Week #75
attributes.description: Jack, Michael and Joel bring you a delicious batch of gaming news, information and more. Who will survive in this week's AHWU

attributes.title: Week #77
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver the goods in this week's brand new AHWU. Join them as they run through the list of games that'll be hitting this week. Finally! More games!

attributes.title: Week #78
attributes.description: Jack and Michael take you on a wondrous journey through the land of AHWU. Will they find the candy mountain full of this week's releases Will they stumble across Crimson Alliance, Resistance 3, Driver: San Franciso, Tiger Woods 12 and more Watch and find out!

attributes.title: Week #79
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff take you through another week of fun times in today's AHWU. Join them on an epic journey through sights, sounds and release dates.

attributes.title: Week #80
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are back with another week of awesomeness. This week they look at F1 something and Gears of War 3. Also stay tuned until the end of the episode for a way to earn 1600 just for playing Gears 3!

attributes.title: Week #81
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver the goods in this week's AHWU. They'll go over this week's releases as well as some news in Mortal Kombat, Star Wars: The Old Republic and more! Stay tuned to see the winner of our Gears of War 3 fail contest!

attributes.title: Week #82
attributes.description: Jack flies solo in this Universal Studios-themed AHWU. Join him on his journey across a theme park dispersing information on this week's releases. Also, keep an eye out for a room full of Full Sail students!

attributes.title: Week #83
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver a dose of goodness in this week's AHWU. Check out a ton of releases hitting this week including Red Dead Redemption, Kinectimals: Bears, Crimson Alliance DLC and more! Also, special guest appearance from Griffon!

attributes.title: Week #84
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff wade through another week full of releases to bring you the best of the best, talk gaming, NBA, Need for Speed and more! You love it because they love you.

attributes.title: Week #85
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you another week's worth of games including Battlefield 3 and World of Warcraft News! Pet Battles FTW!

attributes.title: Week #86
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff have a very SPOOOKY AHWU for you today. By "spooky" I mean there is literally nothing different. At all. HOW SPOOKY! Enjoy today's news about Uncharted 3, Apples to Apples and more!

attributes.title: Week #87
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff bring you a heaping helping of AHWU! This week Geoff pours through a huge list of games including Modern Warfare 3 and Jack announces a brand new GAMEFAILS CONTEST where you can win free games! Watch and learn more!

attributes.title: Week #88
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff put together a brand new AHWU amidst the busiest week of the gaming year.  Holy crap there are a lot of games coming out this week.

attributes.title: Week #89
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff have a pre-Thanksgiving AHWU where they discuss games. Yup. Games... lots of them.

attributes.title: Week #90
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff fight off the Thanksgiving hangover with a fresh new AHWU!

attributes.title: Week #92
attributes.description:
Geoff is out on vacation so Joel steps in to screw up things with Jack.  Watch as they talk about this week in DLC and announce a new contest to win free shirts from http://insertcoinclothing.com !!

Also, you can now pick up your own Rage Quit shirt!  Click here: http://bit.ly/RageQuitShirt

attributes.title: Week #93
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff deliver you the pre-Christmas news and game info from their home offices on the North Pole.  Just kidding, they are really in Austin.  Don't forget to submit your Achievement Hunter Holiday themed image to info@achievementhunter.com with the subject "AH Holidays!"  Also, the Rage Quit shirt is available now right here: http://bit.ly/RageQuitShirt

attributes.title: Holiday Special!
attributes.description: Jack and Geoff are on vacation, so enjoy this collection of submissions to our AH Holidays contest!  See you next year!
